{"type":"text","timestamp":1778464259786,"sessionID":"ses_1eb4a4c05ffeEk6WcdRd6wfRh1","part":{"id":"prt_e14baf345001fmr10kPKLPp51a","messageID":"msg_e14bae93b001L3twGnburZF3cF","sessionID":"ses_1eb4a4c05ffeEk6WcdRd6wfRh1","type":"text","text":"I have completed the work on issue #31961. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Issue:** Obsolete GO:0008785 \"alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity\" and replace it with GO:0102039 \"NADH-dependent peroxiredoxin activity\".\n\n**Actions taken:**\n- Loaded the `term-obsoletion` skill and followed its instructions.\n- Ran pre-validation (`robot reason -r ELK` and SPARQL checks) — all passed.\n- Searched for the terms in the ontology and identified three related stanzas.\n- Obsoleted **GO:0008785**:\n  - Renamed to `obsolete alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity`\n  - Prefixed definition with `OBSOLETE.`\n  - Removed `is_a` logical axiom\n  - Added `is_obsolete: true` and `replaced_by: GO:0102039`\n  - Added comment explaining reason for obsoletion\n  - Added term_tracker_item for issue #31961\n- Updated **GO:0009321** comment to reference the replacement term GO:0102039 instead of GO:0008785.\n- Removed an erroneous comment from **GO:0070937** (CRD-mediated mRNA stability complex) that incorrectly referenced GO:0008785.\n- Checked in the edits.\n- Ran post-validation (`robot reason -r ELK` and SPARQL checks) — all passed.\n- Committed `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` with a detailed message.\n- Created `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md` and `PR_COMMENTS.md` in the working directory.\n\n**Files created (not committed):**\n- `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md`\n- `PR_COMMENTS.md`\n\n**Files committed:**\n- `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`","time":{"start":1778464256837,"end":1778464259784}}}
